title: Reformist leaders resign
new-page: true 
subtitle: Reformist disagreements with our policies have grown too severe.
tags: event
view-if: reformist_dissent >= 60
on-arrival: {!
if (Q.reformist_strength < 10) {
    Q.workers_spd -= 4; 
    Q.new_middle_spd -= 2; 
    Q.old_middle_spd -= 2; 
    Q.rural_spd -= 2; 
    Q.rb_strength -= 200; 
} else if (Q.reformist_strength < 25) {
    Q.workers_spd -= 5; 
    Q.new_middle_spd -= 3; 
    Q.old_middle_spd -= 3; 
    Q.rural_spd -= 3; 
    Q.rb_strength -= 250; 
} else if (Q.reformist_strength < 40) {
    Q.workers_spd -= 6; 
    Q.new_middle_spd -= 4; 
    Q.old_middle_spd -= 4; 
    Q.rural_spd -= 4; 
    Q.rb_strength -= 300; 
} else if (Q.reformist_strength < 60) {
    Q.workers_spd -= 8; 
    Q.new_middle_spd -= 6; 
    Q.old_middle_spd -= 6; 
    Q.rural_spd -= 6; 
    Q.rb_strength -= 350; 
} else {
    Q.workers_spd -= 10; 
    Q.new_middle_spd -= 8; 
    Q.old_middle_spd -= 8; 
    Q.rural_spd -= 8; 
    Q.rb_strength -= 400; 
}

Q.reformist_strength *= 0.3; 

Q.n_advisors_start = Q.n_advisors; 
if (Q.braun_advisor == 1) Q.n_advisors -= 1; 
if (Q.severing_advisor == 1) Q.n_advisors -= 1; 
Q.braun_advisor = 0; 
Q.severing_advisor = 0; 
Q.reformists_resign = 1; 
if (Q.n_advisors < Q.n_advisors_start) Q.shuffle_leadership_timer = 0;
!}
go-to: nspd_formed if ((Q.reformist_strength / 0.3) > 25)
max-visits: 1

= Reformist leaders resign

Our policy choices have greatly offended the reformist faction. Many of our most experienced leaders have [? if ((Q.reformist_strength / 0.3) <= 25) : resigned. ?][? if ((Q.reformist_strength / 0.3) > 25) : moved away to form a new party, the <span style="color: #ff6699;">NSPD (New Social Democratic Party of Germany)</span>. They might pose a risk to us, depending on current <span style="color: #000000;">rep</span><span style="color: #DD0000;">ubl</span><span style="color: #FFCC00;">ican</span> moods. Many of our grassroot members have switched parties. This does not pose a good future for us. ?]
